Description: Westchester Tower Apartment Homes in College Park, Maryland 20740, a smoke free community that offers pet friendly living close to DC. Our apartment homes feature fully equipped kitchens with pantries, floor to ceiling windows, and walk in closets. Some apartment homes have a private patio or balcony, panoramic views and kitchens with GE appliances. Our community amenities include a pool, fitness room, clubroom with wide screen TV, free Wi Fi access, on site recycling, controlled access, PackagePal package delivery system and detached garage parking. We are located in a prime College Park location surrounded by an 1,100 acre National Park. Easy access to I 95, I 495, I 295, the University of Maryland and downtown DC. We are close to shopping, dining, entertainment and recreation. Guarantors welcome!

We welcome your cats and dogs, up to two pets per apartment, and a full-grown maximum weight limit of 75 pounds each. *Breed restrictions apply. Description: Mazza Grandmarc, the best selection in University of Maryland Off-Campus Housing, is located minutes from UMD. Just a short trip down Route One takes you from your front door to class. Mazza GrandMarc features a dedicated stop on Shuttle UM, the official UMD shuttle servicing Maryland students. The community also features a free bike rental program MGM Rides that allows you to bike using the Paint Branch Trail directly from your apartment to campus go green! Mazza GrandMarc is located less than a mile from the DC Metro system, MARC trains, and the Capital Beltway Interstate 495. You can stay connected to Maryland, the District of Columbia, and northern Virginia without ever setting foot in a car! Everything you need and want is within walking distance: Groceries, banking, fast food, restaurants, night life, the post office, fun attractions and much more!

Description:
5 Bed/ 2 Bath house available walking distance from UMD in a quiet and safe neighborhood. 
Just reduced $150! Now for $3100/month plus utilities for the whole house! We can also offer $1950 plus utilities for 3 rooms. Smaller groups or individuals: please contact us so we can can connect you with other potential roommates who are interested in this house. We encourage you to use the roommate finder option on the OCH website and form your own group of 5.
Furnished options available for a higher rent. For every $100 of higher monthly rent ($1200/year), we will install furniture worth $1800. Our interior decorators do a great job - please check out airbnb dot com/rooms/17007505 to see our only furnished short-term rental in College Park.
The house is located on 36th Ave off-Metzerott Road in College Park - a 10-15 mins walk to the heart of campus. It is a 4 mins walk to Courtyards Exp, Adelphi and Purple shuttle stops. The Courtyards shuttle runs every 15 minutes and the Purple runs till 4 AM in the morning. 
All three upstairs bedrooms have newly finished hardwood floors. The basement rooms have new carpets.
All bedrooms have smoke alarms. The house conforms to the city code for rental properties.
The house comes with a Washer/Dryer, Central A/C and Gas Heating. 
The driveway can park 3-4 cars and more off-street. It also has a large yard maintained by the management. One month's security deposit required at the time of lease signing.
Please call/text/email for details. You can call or text us anytime (really!) at 240-294-3535 or email help.artemisia@gmail.com if you have any questions.

Description:
NOW SHOWING! Our last available 5 Bedroom /2 Bath house. 
Walking distance from the University of Maryland campus and the College Park Metro Station. The house is also next to a UM Shuttle stop. There's a bike trail next to the house that goes to campus. 
Furnished options available for a higher rent ($100 higher for fully furnished). Our interior decorators do a great job. Please check out airbnb com/rooms/17007505 to see our only furnished short-term rental in College Park.
Yard maintenance provided by the property management company.
There is central heating and air-conditioning and a working fireplace in the living room. 
Please call/text/email for details. You can call or text us anytime (really!) at 240-294-3535 or email help.artemisia@gmail.com if you have any questions.

(240) 206-6044 x116 - Location! Location! Location .... This is a spacious and private room that is suitable for a College Student or working professional, conveniently located close to UMD, close to 495, Major roads and shopping. This is a room within a beautiful house that features an open floor plan. There is shared common space, kitchenette and rear entrance. Washer and Dryer on site. All Utilities are included! Cable and Internet is also included as a BONUS! Nice flat back yard.
(RLNE2586766) Other Amenities - Basement. Appliances - Dishwasher, Refrigerator- Electric, Range, Oven, Garbage Disposal, Washer & Dryer, Other- Water Heater, Ice-maker,, Microwave. Lease lengths - 12 Months, 24 Months. Accessibility features - Clear Floor Area in Front of Sink and Range. Description: Brand new student housing in College Park, MD. Landmark is designed to provide students with the home they aspire to have as young professionals! Our interiors are modern and minimalistic with clean lines and bold colors. Units are fully furnished with in-unit washer/dryer. Stainless steel appliances & quartz kitchen countertops and modern Euro-style cabinetry. 50" Flat screen living room TV. High-speed internet service & premium cable and residents have free access to all amenities! Landmark gives students the freedom of their own apartment while still maintaining the communal spirit of UMD residence halls. Equipped with only the most state-of-the-art security technology including electronic key access and a smartphone guest admittance app to enable the most comprehensive and convenient security protocol. Located directly across the street from the UMD campus and adjacent to the stores and restaurants on Baltimore Avenue. Students have the convenience of a short walk to class, entertainment hotspots or the College Park metro station.
